and more!

00:04:30.030 --> 00:04:35.290
Additionally, 5.4 adds Speaker Gulan - he
sells you a Censer of Eteranl Agony, which

00:04:35.290 --> 00:04:39.540
allows you to become hostile to all players
including your faction, and kill them for

00:04:39.540 --> 00:04:43.720
Bloody Coins, which are used to purchase several
items, including a mount.

00:04:43.720 --> 00:04:48.220
As for World Changes, the Vale of Eternal
Blossoms has been drained dry of any water,

00:04:48.220 --> 00:04:51.160
and corruption has spread across most of the
Vale.

00:04:51.160 --> 00:04:55.460
This damage included the destruction of the
Golden Pagoda, so you won't be able to do

00:04:55.460 --> 00:04:57.870
the Golden Lotus daily quests anymore.

00:04:57.870 --> 00:05:02.520
Moonfang is a new boss added to teh Darkmoon
Faire in patch 5.4 - he drops a new mount,

00:05:02.520 --> 00:05:05.880
pet, transmog weapon, and a few novelty items.

